      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Mar 2025 21:44:41 +0000</pubDate>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Today is my last day at Google. I joined as an intern almost 18 years ago, and it still feels like it was yesterday. I&amp;#39;m incredibly grateful that I got to work with so many amazing and talented folks, but I&amp;#39;m also excited (and terrified!) to try something new. First step: a few months of travel and photography :)&lt;/p&gt;</description>
